{"tid":1841831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】高雄男隱匿病情赴舞廳　台灣重罰30萬　女服務生隔離中","createTime":"2020-01-25T11:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T15:12:52.000Z","uid":209657,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"da7788331b155aeca4ba47ee1f305cd97f872c88","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:56:12.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續擴大，中央流行疫情指揮中心召開記者會說明武漢肺炎最新進度，並表示中一例確診的男台商，曾在22日下午4時至6時曾經到過高雄市苓雅區金巴黎舞廳（招牌為金芭黎），且全程未配戴口罩；高雄市衛生局指出，今(25)日凌晨3時，一名舞廳女服務生出現病徵，緊急通報衛生所，目前已在醫院隔離，並做進一步檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市衛生局指出，該名個案入境前即有發燒及上呼吸道等症狀，<span style=\"color: red;\">並在大陸就醫服藥</span>；1月21日入境時，個案因服藥退燒未被機場發燒篩檢站攔檢，也未主動向檢疫人員告知有症狀及武漢活動史，就搭乘捷運返回住家，但在搭乘大眾交通工具的過程中，都有配戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n由於該名確診台商，曾在22日下午4時，前往金巴黎舞廳（招牌為金芭黎），<span style=\"color: red;\">全程未戴口罩</span>；高雄市衛生局簡任技正潘炤穎指出，目前高雄需要追蹤的人數，不包括搭機及捷運的人數約80人，同時有一名與該名確診台商接觸的人出現病徵。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市衛生局指出，出現病徵的民眾為金巴黎舞廳的女服務生，於今(25)日凌晨3時，出現呼吸急促、咳嗽的情形，想起前兩天的客人曾說自己從武漢返台，因而主動通報衛生所，衛生局派救護車將該名女服務生送往醫院進一步檢驗，目前仍在醫院隔離，還有待報告出爐。"},{"pid":"fac0c9acac7f767eca36f5f0a9dbcba60efb3822","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:57:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=678593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D678593&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=1ee97d8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D678593&h=aed54230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=678593</a>"},{"pid":"bdbe67df04444ca074b1b1ac114a981c94287365","tid":1841831,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:57:51.000Z","msg":"好彩台女醒目篤佢出黎"},{"pid":"ca67ed92b97657a3ec79a4da83d3f5d1dcd51de0","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/01/25/2377613-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F01%2F25%2F2377613-XXL.jpg&h=2c2eb313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n知情人士透露，金巴黎舞廳的前身是「金蒂」，裡頭的舞小姐人數達200至300人，會在競爭激烈的市場中脫穎而出，除了舞小姐陣容堅強外，主要是原因是價格較其他家低廉。"},{"pid":"2a74f4a0905d478ef70ca3b3cf58e51713f0cdd9","tid":1841831,"uid":8410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:59:16.000Z","msg":"發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e330336bd7bf9c1c69bc3482ada9f74c02d75772","tid":1841831,"uid":230416,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:01:41.000Z","msg":"舞廳人流咁大，台灣可以準備收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da017c00b1ae71608e6edec7cec00aa9bb117cfb","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e330336bd7bf9c1c69bc3482ada9f74c02d75772","tid":1841831,"uid":230416,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:01:41.000Z","msg":"舞廳人流咁大，台灣可以準備收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"都係廢老韓粉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fa275614f4fe34aacbfc84e74edc41ec65c877","tid":1841831,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:09:06.000Z","msg":"叫雞啲雞都怕咗你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe15653e8788a28ad123a7ceb3123bbbb1946ad5","tid":1841831,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:10:22.000Z","msg":"姓韓條垃圾去左邊"},{"pid":"33db17e7df7bb27a7f53ef62c466a69c71c117d8","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe15653e8788a28ad123a7ceb3123bbbb1946ad5","tid":1841831,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:10:22.000Z","msg":"姓韓條垃圾去左邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"放年假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506ad7acde7e1b6607bfe8f241f0f87deef40747","tid":1841831,"uid":54486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"同黃秋生伊波拉一樣，一返屋企就去叫雞"},{"pid":"811c9538893903ac9edbe15a5446009af68dabf7","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdbe67df04444ca074b1b1ac114a981c94287365","tid":1841831,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T11:57:51.000Z","msg":"好彩台女醒目篤佢出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:36:22.000Z","msg":"據悉，該名服務生於今（25）日凌晨，先感覺到不舒服，才去打電話給台商「逼問出有去過武漢」，才趕緊主動通報就醫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc5227c046f4ea618d6680297612fc63dc3fb99","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:38:17.000Z","msg":"金芭黎舞廳營業時間從下午2時開始，下午至晚間9時是所謂「茶舞」，可供民眾前往跳舞，這時段內最多會有2、300個小姐上班，平均一個大班大約帶20個左右的小姐，每小時坐檯費760元、茶資2、300元，吸引許多在地民眾前往消費。"},{"pid":"490b707965745772091edcd9a526e4cb9fe50538","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/GaITc4fXLLX_rZlpwdeQ2CF4uTc=/760x427/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/QT5AMUYBILYVNNGJNWNW4LUPPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FGaITc4fXLLX_rZlpwdeQ2CF4uTc%3D%2F760x427%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FQT5AMUYBILYVNNGJNWNW4LUPPQ.jpg&h=ad97c742&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下午原要進舞廳上班的舞小姐，在得知武漢肺炎男台商曾光顧，在門外竊竊私語討論是否要進舞廳上班。"},{"pid":"5d64e08d7be2ba84fd9baec8d4d99556c9a820af","tid":1841831,"uid":46758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:40:51.000Z","msg":"台女醒目過人"},{"pid":"db550c16931a2ce59db88fbc0153f25ebf57dddc","tid":1841831,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:44:06.000Z","msg":"民主是個好東西"},{"pid":"3040dd61db2dc3145f2bb2050be3c592fec1dc05","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:49:05.000Z","msg":"高雄市衛生局表示，這名台商住在左營區，1月20日在中國武漢時出現呼吸道症狀，在當地就醫吃藥，隔天21日晚間6點多從武漢搭機抵達高雄小港機場，晚間7點半到8點許，從小港機場站搭高雄捷運到巨蛋站下車。"},{"pid":"4911627ce36ca75ce3ea216d34c4086e1fcf55b2","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"衛生局指出，這名台商22日下午到高雄某醫院皮膚科掛診，下午4點到6點與朋友一同到金芭黎舞廳，23日他到左營某耳鼻喉科診所就醫，才告知醫師曾去過武漢，醫師有警覺通報，這名台商才被安排住進負壓隔離病房。<br />\n<br />\n這名台商住進負壓隔離病房，24日檢驗確診感染武漢肺炎，但對於防疫人員詢問他的活動史，都未說出曾去過金芭黎舞廳與某醫院皮膚科，直到今天一名舞小姐主動通報，他才坦承。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a07877e4e5e29b7989af637501dde7620cc6f9e","tid":1841831,"uid":224659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:53:52.000Z","msg":"唔敢認自己叫雞"},{"pid":"e67ba35613c23d099f69c90c9486195bf30f787f","tid":1841831,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"死前叫下雞"},{"pid":"01be4789999ce50bb6e27acb57862f88384268fc","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e67ba35613c23d099f69c90c9486195bf30f787f","tid":1841831,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"死前叫下雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫大陸雞"},{"pid":"c31dbf5f5d0a8caa2f57ac8daa31e69233d99ade","tid":1841831,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01be4789999ce50bb6e27acb57862f88384268fc","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e67ba35613c23d099f69c90c9486195bf30f787f","tid":1841831,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"死前叫下雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫大陸雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係大陸雞"},{"pid":"919f6adf1280d59793f619ebc92d194a5f582c19","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c31dbf5f5d0a8caa2f57ac8daa31e69233d99ade","tid":1841831,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01be4789999ce50bb6e27acb57862f88384268fc","tid":1841831,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e67ba35613c23d099f69c90c9486195bf30f787f","tid":1841831,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"死前叫下雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:02:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫大陸雞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係大陸雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"係咩以為台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f08c4da2e60b21afda0582e3504664c716e0f3","tid":1841831,"uid":116609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"60fa275614f4fe34aacbfc84e74edc41ec65c877","tid":1841831,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:09:06.000Z","msg":"叫雞啲雞都怕咗你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}